{"tid":2077440,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"近6成網民投票 美斯應被逐","createTime":"2020-06-24T09:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T11:05:39.000Z","uid":72497,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"970a7042800cb4d8cb26ca47b60c345ba6ba6462","tid":2077440,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿周二晚主場1:0小勝畢爾包，暫時重返西甲榜首，但賽後焦點落在球王美斯下半場腳踩對手足踝的一幕，逃過球證法眼，而引起熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n事發在69分鐘，畢爾包後衛耶禮艾華利斯（Yeray Alvarez）在己隊禁區頂瞓身解圍，來遲一步的美斯（Lionel Messi）右腳踩中對手足踝犯規，耶禮艾華利斯狀甚痛苦，球證曼辛奴立即吹罰，但沒有出示紅牌，甚至黃牌警告美斯，VAR也沒有介入翻看事發片段。2分鐘後，美斯有份參與的攻勢，最終由拉傑迪為巴塞射入奠定勝局的一球。 賽後，《馬卡報》舉辦網上投票，超過1400人投票下，有58%的網民認為美斯這次粗野動作，應要被罰紅牌。"},{"pid":"fc54d6b43d936f11f1074182b5af412312ccae9a","tid":2077440,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"啲網民都唔撚識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcb8f203987eba6f8c816285651fe8e5fe753b6","tid":2077440,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"58%蝗狗"},{"pid":"2b07c970d0ce54eeb38f83586831ca7d11c2a798","tid":2077440,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3084255b811bc926cd83c38c65f5544f1b5a59cf","tid":2077440,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdcb8f203987eba6f8c816285651fe8e5fe753b6","tid":2077440,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"58%蝗狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"又迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23489521e201f2a05ba79ffc6cb1665c45c68ce","tid":2077440,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"馬卡報最中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de26444d1539db836b0e1405f7fd361